I've heard Lisbon's historic center is gorgeous but wondering if Cuauhtémoc in Mexico City might be more affordable overall. I'm bringing my electric car to Texas first and driving part way, then flying. Concerned about time differences for client calls too. Which city would give me better value with highly-rated accommodations and authentic local experience? I'd love to see what kind of places I could actually get in each spot.
